tip_0: Dodging her Crescent Strike will lower her damage output significantly after level 6.
tip_1: Her Shield lasts for only a short while, so wait until it wears out and harass her after.
tip_2: By using a knock-up (e.g. Blitzcrank's Power Fist) and/or displacement (Tristana's Buster Shot) while she is using her ultimate on a marked target will deny her a reset on her ultimate.
